(197, 60, 14, '14\nSWOTIFY\nTechnical\ndefinition:\nit\nis\na\nspecific\nevaluation\nframework\nand\nan\ninitiative\nby\nthe\nCentral\nStudent\nGovernment\norganization.\nIt\nis\nderived\nfrom\nthe\nSWOT\nanalysis\nwhich\nutilizes\nthe\ndetermination\nof\nStrengths,\nWeaknesses,\nOpportunities,\nand\nThreats\nrelated\nto\nthe\nappraisal\nand\nassessment\nof\nfellow\nofficers.\nOperational\ndefinition:\ndependent\nvariable\nof\nthe\nsentiment\nanalysis;\na\nplatform\nto\nbe\nutilized\nfor\nsentiment\nanalysis.\nConceptual\nFramework\nINPUT\nKnowledge\nRequirements \n1.\nTextual\ndata \nfrom\nevaluation,\nassessment,\nand\nfeedback \nin\nthe\nprocess\nSWOTIFY\nTools\n1.\nNatural\nLanguage\nProcessing \n2.\nLexicon \n3.\nStop\nwords \n4.\nNatural\nLanguage\nToolkit \n5.\nMachine\nLearning\n→\nPROCESS\nData\nCollection\nGathering\ntextual\ndata\nusing\nthe\nplatform \nSWOTIFY\nby\nmanual\ndownloading\nof\nevaluation.\nPreprocessing \nCleaning\nand\npreparation\nof\ntextual\ndata \nby\nremoving\nnoise,\nspecial\ncharacters,\nand \nirrelevant\ninformation.\nTokenization\nby\nsegmenting\ntext\ninto \ntokens\nand\ntransforming\nwords\ninto\ntheir \nfundamental\nor\nbase\nforms\nto\ndecrease \ndimensionality . \nStemming\ntextual\ndata\nby\nreducing \nsuffixes\nor\nprefixes\nto\nprevent\nincorrect\nmeaning\nor \nspelling. \nLemmatization\nreduces\nwords\nto\ntheir \ndictionary\nform\nto\nensure\nthat\nthe\nresulting\nwords \nfrom\nthe\ntext\nhave\ndictionary-derived\nmeanings.\nSentiment\nAnalysis\nTechniques \nApply\na\nsentiment\nlexicon\nfor\nsentiment \nanalysis\nbased\non\nrules\n(associating\nwords\nwith \npositive,\nnegative,\nand\nneutral\nsentiments),\nor\ntrain \nmachine\nlearning\nmodels\nfor\na\nmore\ndata-driven \napproach\nto\nsentiment\nanalysis.\nAggregation\nand\nScoring \nCombine\nsentiment\nscores\neither\nat\nthe \ndocument\nor\nsentence\nlevel.\nCompute\na \ncomprehensive\nsentiment\nscore\nfor\nthe\nentire \ndataset\nor\nspecific\ncategories\nas\nrequir